rules.description: Press right_shift twice to enter double shift mode, press right_shift once to leave it
alternative num-mode for numbers on home row, and symbols
delete-mode for deleting characters with ui, words with jk and lines with hl
adventure-mode allows for easy back and forth one character, word or line
select-mode = adventure-mode + SHIFT (i.e. selection, not just movement)
w-mode for general shortcuts like browser tab navigation
num-mode for numbers on home row, and symbols
